    "92287930": {
      "title": "The dissolved gases-carbon dioxide",
      "abstract": "A floatable collection device where contaminated liquid such as water polluted by oil is collected into a central drum by means of an elongated spiralled inverted V-shaped trough which is circumferentially mounted on the drum. The device includes expulsion means by which the contaminated liquid is expelled from the drum to separation apparatus located elsewhere for separation of the oil from the water."
